bug_finding.recommendation:
try를 mkstemp 직후로 옮김:
```
fd, tmp = tempfile.mkstemp(dir=str(p.parent), suffix=".tmp")
try:
    with os.fdopen(fd, "w", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        f.write(content)
    os.replace(tmp, str(p))
except Exception:
    try:
        os.close(fd)  # fdopen이 실패한 케이스 보강
    except OSError:
        pass
    try:
        os.unlink(tmp)
    except OSError:
        pass
    raise
```
실 위험은 낮으나 방어적 코드 권고.
